    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蕾雅是一名女高中生，同时也是个超级英雄，每天她都要配合经纪人妮奥对付从异次元涌现的怪物，你将与她们共同迎战强敌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 电光火石般的超级英雄空战一触即发，等你来战！游戏操作直观易上手，每个人都可以成为对战专家。调整摄像头轻松锁定目标，然后按下一个按钮，便可发动猛烈的攻击！迅速投入战场，使出爽快华丽的连击，战斗的热血只需一键就能点燃。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/cc0784a9072acce4afd9ca7709412944.poster.avif?t=1772219713\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/cc0784a9072acce4afd9ca7709412944.webm?t=1772219713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/cc0784a9072acce4afd9ca7709412944.mp4?t=1772219713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自异世界的威胁有小有大，无论是弱小生物还是预料之外的庞大怪兽，与它们的战斗都将十分激烈。在动画风格的对决中使出全力终结敌人，让他们尝尝撞上地板和墙壁的滋味吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/9f5cf7acbf4999ae85a6717ac7cba2ca.poster.avif?t=1772219713\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/9f5cf7acbf4999ae85a6717ac7cba2ca.webm?t=1772219713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/9f5cf7acbf4999ae85a6717ac7cba2ca.mp4?t=1772219713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随故事中角色的脚步，身临其境地体验有趣欢快的英雄主播的冒险！时尚的女主角、个性丰富的配角与设计新颖的敌人是本游戏的最大特色。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/3e985b31f5b86ea6aa70ffc6b4db854d.poster.avif?t=1772219713\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/3e985b31f5b86ea6aa70ffc6b4db854d.webm?t=1772219713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/3e985b31f5b86ea6aa70ffc6b4db854d.mp4?t=1772219713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 种标志性武器，30 多种独特动作和攻击方式。充分发挥他们的长处，施展特殊连击与令人瞠目的终结技，将敌人一网打尽吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/ad3cf95672d0e36b2594bdbf9582052c.poster.avif?t=1772219713\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/ad3cf95672d0e36b2594bdbf9582052c.webm?t=1772219713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/ad3cf95672d0e36b2594bdbf9582052c.mp4?t=1772219713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索 38 个关卡，直面 24 种敌人，其中还有强力 boss！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/7dbfc6dc03bf95ba965467b33e1f3a58.poster.avif?t=1772219713\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/7dbfc6dc03bf95ba965467b33e1f3a58.webm?t=1772219713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077640/extras/7dbfc6dc03bf95ba965467b33e1f3a58.mp4?t=1772219713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>日漫风格，震撼人心的英雄动作冒险等你体验！</strong></p>",
